block-type=\"core\"><a href=\"http://podplayer.net/?podId=2447675\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/podcast-addict-for-windows-pc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-66450\" //></a></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-woa-wordpress-on-air-n-14\" data-block-type=\"core\">WOA : WordPress On Air N°14</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Fin de l&rsquo;année 2021, c&rsquo;est l&rsquo;occasion de prendre des nouvelles de nos anciens invités. Nous avons enregistré cet épisode bonus en live en présence de certains auditeurs et plusieurs de nos anciens invités. Rachel et JB ont tenté de nous coller avec un petit quizz WordPress et nous avons pris des nouvelles de chacun de nos invités.  </p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\" data-block-type=\"core\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-nos-invites\" data-block-type=\"core\">Nos invités</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" data-block-type=\"core\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\" data-block-type=\"core\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/olivier-gorzalka.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"73062\" data-full-url=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/olivier-gorzalka.jpg\" data-link=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/woa-12-maintenance-eco-conception/olivier-gorzalka/\" class=\"wp-image-73062\" //><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Olivier Gorzalka</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img width=\"960\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/stephanie_vachon.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"73061\" data-full-url=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/stephanie_vachon.jpeg\" data-link=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/woa-12-maintenance-eco-conception/stephanie_vachon/\" class=\"wp-image-73061\" //><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Stéphanie Vachon</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img width=\"395\" height=\"395\" src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/alexandre-derocq.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"72502\" data-full-url=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/alexandre-derocq.jpeg\" data-link=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/woa-11-parlons-newsletter-avec-acymailing/alexandre-derocq/\" class=\"wp-image-72502\" //><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Alexandre Derocq</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img width=\"400\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/loic-blascos.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"72051\" data-full-url=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/loic-blascos.jpg\" data-link=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/woa-1-le-podcast-wordpress-de-lagence-whodunit/loic-blascos/\" class=\"wp-image-72051\" //><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Loïc Blascos</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img width=\"430\" height=\"440\" src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/lycia-diaz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"71942\" data-full-url=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/lycia-diaz.jpg\" data-link=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/woa-8-le-podcast-wordpress-de-agence-whodunit/lycia-diaz/\" class=\"wp-image-71942\" //><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Lycia Diaz.</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img width=\"396\" height=\"396\" src=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/nicolas-mercatili.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"71937\" data-full-url=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/nicolas-mercatili.jpeg\" data-link=\"https://www.whodunit.fr/woa-9-le-podcast-wordpress-de-lagence-whodunit/nicolas-mercatili/\" class=\"wp-image-71937\" //><figc